q: What is Compute the Future's expected weekly time commitment?
a: Compute the Future's expected weekly time commitment varies based on your program choice. You sign up for sessions either on campus after school during the week from 3:30 to 4:30 PM or virtually on Saturdays.

q: How can I contact Compute the Future with any questions?
a: Our Support is available 7 days a week and you can email us at admin@computefutures.org.
